{"about_the_game":"Operation Valor is a tactical top-down multiplayer shooter that provides large-scale combat through base building and teamwork. Players will fight across diverse battlefields with squad-based action in vehicles, or on foot. Prepare for an exciting battle utilizing strategy, logistics, and base building. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Firefight-Kalinsk.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/TAKE_UP_ARMS.png?t=1698482284\" /><br><br>Every soldier matters. Good teamwork and communication is essential to win. Using unique roles, soldiers can work together to manage resources, deploy necessary vehicles, build strategic forward operating bases, and lead others into battle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Building.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/SEIZE_THE_DAY.png?t=1698482284\" /><br><br>Advance to the frontlines in 27 vs 27 head-to-head combat. Decide your loadout from any of the 7 distinct infantry roles and take advantage of crucial equipment and different weapons. Fight as a Squad Leader, Rifleman, Medic, Support, Marksman, Demolition, or Engineer alongside your squad members. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Explosions.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/SUPPLY_YOUR_FRONTLINE.png?t=1698482284\" /><br><br>Resource management is key to continue fighting your opponent. A logistics vehicle can hold both construction points and ammo. Construction points allow squad leaders to place down offensive and defensive buildings, and ammo can be gathered by soldiers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Vehicles.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/MORE_INFO.png?t=1698482284\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Release Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> At least 3 maps<br></li><li> Buildable objects that will give you an advantage on the battlefield<br></li><li> Light vehicles (MRAP and Logi Truck)<br></li><li> Team specific weapons<br></li><li> Class specific weapons including the mine, satchel charge, RPG, repair wrench, medic bag, etc.<br></li><li> Stats and Leaderboards <br></li><li> Ranks</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1698482284","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/page.bg.jpg?t=1698482284","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1698482284","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1698482284","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Contains guns, shooting other players/violence, explosions, and blood.  May contain cursing voice lines. "},"demos":[{"appid":1107960,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>JOIN THE COMMUNITY ON DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Operation Valor is a tactical top-down multiplayer shooter that provides large-scale combat through base building and teamwork. Players will fight across diverse battlefields with squad-based action in vehicles, or on foot. Prepare for an exciting battle utilizing strategy, logistics, and base building. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Firefight-Kalinsk.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/TAKE_UP_ARMS.png?t=1698482284\" /><br><br>Every soldier matters. Good teamwork and communication is essential to win. Using unique roles, soldiers can work together to manage resources, deploy necessary vehicles, build strategic forward operating bases, and lead others into battle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Building.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/SEIZE_THE_DAY.png?t=1698482284\" /><br><br>Advance to the frontlines in 27 vs 27 head-to-head combat. Decide your loadout from any of the 7 distinct infantry roles and take advantage of crucial equipment and different weapons. Fight as a Squad Leader, Rifleman, Medic, Support, Marksman, Demolition, or Engineer alongside your squad members. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/24F-OperationValor-Explosions.gif?t=1698482284\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1095480/extras/SUPPLY_YOUR_FRONTLINE.png?t=1698482284\" /><br><br>Resource management is key to continue fighting your opponent. A logistics vehicle can hold both construction points and ammo. Construction points allow squad leaders to place down offensive and defensive buildings, and ammo can be gathered by soldiers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass